race.comment: MANDELA HAYZE (7) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 0.8 lengths away in second (25.64) at Q Lakeside in a Mix 5 over 457m. Hard to beat again. CANYA HAMMER (1) hasn't been far away here at the last two, finding the frame both times, most recently when second beaten a nose (20.12). Bold showing expected. ICY HOT (2) has claims fresh from a recent placing at big odds.
